OL,3,CMan arrested and murder investigation
OL,4,Claunched after woman in her 80s dies
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a woman in her 80s was
OL,8,Ffound dead in Cornwall.
OL,10,FPolice were called soon after midnight
OL,11,Fon Friday 29 May after the woman was
OL,12,Ffound at a property in the Ashton
OL,13,Farea, near Helston.
OL,15,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,16,Finvestigation and a 36-year-old man
OL,17,Fremains in police custody.
OL,19,FWe have launched a murder
OL,20,Finvestigation following the death of a
OL,21,Fwoman near Helston.
