OL,3,CMan arrested and murder investigation
OL,4,Claunched after woman in her 80s dies
OL,6,FThe woman's next of kin have been
OL,7,Finformed.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Pete Gee said: "A
OL,10,Fpolice cordon has been established at
OL,11,Fthe scene and enquiries are ongoing.
OL,13,F"At this time, I would like to
OL,14,Freassure the community that incidents
OL,15,Fof this nature are very rare but if
OL,16,Fanyone has any concerns, I encourage
OL,17,Fthem to approach and speak to our
OL,18,Fofficers.
OL,26,@qD@dOUuD@AOU
