OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780315873
OL,3,CMan arrested and murder investigation
OL,4,Claunched after woman in her 80s dies
OL,6,F"A heightened police presence is
OL,7,Fexpected to remain in the area over
OL,8,Fthe next few days as enquiries are
OL,9,Fongoing."
